        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "Arbor wine that has been aged for several years\u2014or artificially aged with alchemy\u2014develops both a greater complexity of flavor and a stronger connection to nature. When you drink aged arbor wine, vegetation in a 20-foot emanation around you begins to writhe, becoming difficult terrain until the start of your next turn.",
